import React from 'react'
import BigDisplay from '../components/BigDisplay'
import Content from '../components/Content'
import TextField from '../components/TextField'
import Button from '../components/Button'
import ConfirmationLabel from '../components/ConfirmationLabel'

import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container'
import Row from 'react-bootstrap/Row'
import Col from 'react-bootstrap/Col'

export default (props) =>
    <>
        <BigDisplay className="bg-white"
            title="Summary"
            subTitle="Please check your details below before submitting."
        />
        
        <Content className="bg-pink">
            <ConfirmationLabel />
            <TextField readOnly={true} label="Brand Name/ DBA" />
            <TextField readOnly={true} label="Online Store Website" />
            <TextField readOnly={true} label="Business Owner Email" />
            <TextField readOnly={true} label="Federal Tax Classification" />
            <TextField readOnly={true} label="Tax Identification Number" />
        </Content>

        <Content className="bg-green">
            <TextField readOnly={true} label="Legal Name of the Company" />
            <TextField readOnly={true} label="Street Number and Steet Name" />
            <TextField readOnly={true} label="Postal Code" />
            <TextField readOnly={true} label="City" />
            <TextField readOnly={true} label="Country" />
            <TextField readOnly={true} label="Province of Incorporation" />
        </Content>

        <Content>
            <TextField readOnly={true} label="First Name" />
            <TextField readOnly={true} label="Last Name" />
            <TextField readOnly={true} label="Date of Birth" />
            <TextField readOnly={true} label="Residential Address" />
            <TextField readOnly={true} label="Postal Code" />
            <TextField readOnly={true} label="City" />
            <TextField readOnly={true} label="Country" />
        </Content>


        <Content className="bg-pink">
            <TextField readOnly={true} label="Currency" />
            <TextField readOnly={true} label="Country" />
            <TextField readOnly={true} label="Account Holderâ€™s Name" />
            <TextField readOnly={true} label="Routing Number" />
            <TextField readOnly={true} label="Account Number" />

            <Row className="menuRow">
                <Col md={2} lg={2} sm={1} xs={1}></Col>
                <Col md={6} lg={6} sm={10} xs={10}>
                    <Button >Submit</Button>
                </Col>
                <Col md={4} lg={4} sm={1} xs={1}></Col>
            </Row>
        </Content>

    </>
